title: "Six-Gun Gorilla: Long Days of Vengeance" issue #1
description:
Howdy folks! This is the creator of SIX-GUN GORILLA: LONG DAYS OF VENGEANCE. It recently came to my attention that there was a failed attempt to upload the first issue. Well, here's the real thing!

Just to clarify, this is NOT the SIX-GUN GORILLA by Boom! and Si Spurrier. Mine was published on my blog on June 5th, theirs on June 16th.

I hope you folks enjoy the read!
